        <h1>Paramount&#43; Offered Jerry Seinfeld and Michael Richards $500M for New Sitcom?</h1>
        <h2>Paramount&#39;s willingness to work with the blacklisted Richards shows a &#34;commitment to second chances and creative redemption,&#34; one article said.</h2>
        <div class="author-date-container">
          <h3>By Real Authorington</h3>
          <h2>Published April 18, 2024</h2>
        </div>
